### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

###

### Scraping Service Status
GET http://localhost:3001/api/scrape/status

###

### Scrape Single URL - Costa Rica Store Example
POST http://localhost:3001/api/scrape/url
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://cr.epaenlinea.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=taladro",
  "options": {
    "timeout": 172800000
  }
}

###

### Search for Products
POST http://localhost:3001/api/scrape/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://www.example-store.com/search",
  "searchQuery": "laptop",
  "options": {
    "waitFor": 3000
  }
}

###

### Crawl Site (Multiple Pages)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/scrape/crawl
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://www.example-store.com",
  "options": {
    "timeout": 60000
  }
}

###

### Test with Invalid URL (should fail validation)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/scrape/url
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "not-a-valid-url"
}

###

### Test with Missing URL (should fail validation)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/scrape/url
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "searchQuery": "laptop"
}
